{"TopicId":134293,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Why does everyone care so much about IVA\u0027s","CreatedByName":"OrbitalBuzzsaw","CreatedById":158329,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-15T23:05:42Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"OrbitalBuzzsaw","CreatedById":158329,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-15T23:05:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOkay. So for a while I was wondering, why does everyone care so much about IVAs? I mean, who even uses them? I never fly from them, and they\u0027re downright stupid on my tiny keyboard. The thing I\u0027m particularly annoyed about is that modders refuse to release cockpits until they have IVAs. Seriously, modders!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mastikator","CreatedById":135309,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-15T23:15:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFlying a rocket from IVA can feel more authentic. It would be something else to have VR IVA and all the tools available from the IVA.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Raptor9","CreatedById":67915,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-15T23:16:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA lot of people use them. \u00A0Some people play entire missions solely from IVA. \u00A0I personally love to capture video and photo opportunities using them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRegarding the modders holding back on their work until an IVA is complete, I would venture a guess to say it\u0027s professional pride in their work. \u00A0Take \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/122414-nils277/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022122414\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/122414-nils277/\u0022\u003E@Nils277\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0and \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/133606-105-kerbal-planetary-base-systems-v103-updated-14th-march-16/\u0022\u003EKerbal Planetary Base Systems\u003C/a\u003E mod, all of his IVA\u0027s are absolutely beautiful and bring\u00A0a sense of immersion and completeness to a stock-a-like parts pack. \u00A0I salute him for that. \u00A0Not all modders do this, but I appreciate the ones that do. \u00A0It\u0027s hard work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-03-15T23:17:09Z\u0022 title=\u002203/15/2016 11:17  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 15, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Raptor9\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"razark","CreatedById":32993,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-15T23:36:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nImmersion.\u00A0 It\u0027s great to get that feeling that you\u0027re actually there.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy are you viewing IVAs on your keyboard?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nathair","CreatedById":102894,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-15T23:48:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222458870\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221458083142\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158329\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022OrbitalBuzzsaw\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n39 minutes ago, OrbitalBuzzsaw said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean, who even uses them?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI do. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:kiss:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_kiss.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:kiss:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222458870\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221458083142\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158329\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022OrbitalBuzzsaw\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n40 minutes ago, OrbitalBuzzsaw said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthey\u0027re downright stupid on my tiny keyboard.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t understand either, how are IVAs stupid \u0022on your keyboard\u0022?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Voculus","CreatedById":85437,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T00:11:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUntil you\u0027ve taken off, orbited, and landed back at KSP with only this as your guide, you\u0027ve never spaced, bro! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/PD3OgL1.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022PD3OgL1.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-03-16T00:11:24Z\u0022 title=\u002203/16/2016 12:11  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 16, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Voculus\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OrbitalBuzzsaw","CreatedById":158329,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T00:11:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIVA hotkey is annoying. Trying to pull up, go into IVA. UGH!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222458893\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221458083781\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002267915\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Raptor9\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n55 minutes ago, Raptor9 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA lot of people use them. \u00A0Some people play entire missions solely from IVA. \u00A0I personally love to capture video and photo opportunities using them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRegarding the modders holding back on their work until an IVA is complete, I would venture a guess to say it\u0027s professional pride in their work. \u00A0Take \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/122414-nils277/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022122414\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/122414-nils277/\u0022\u003E@Nils277\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0and \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/133606-105-kerbal-planetary-base-systems-v103-updated-14th-march-16/\u0022\u003EKerbal Planetary Base Systems\u003C/a\u003E mod, all of his IVA\u0027s are absolutely beautiful and bring\u00A0a sense of immersion and completeness to a stock-a-like parts pack. \u00A0I salute him for that. \u00A0Not all modders do this, but I appreciate the ones that do. \u00A0It\u0027s hard work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis I understand, but its a little ridiculous sometimes, as in no BETAS EVEN until a IVA done. Take BahamutoD\u0027s MK22 cockpits. I is wanting, but NO RELEASE BECAUSE OF ASET PROPS. SERIOUSLY.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222458890\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221458083711\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022135309\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mastikator\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n58 minutes ago, Mastikator said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFlying a rocket from IVA can feel more authentic. It would be something else to have VR IVA and all the tools available from the IVA.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0OK that would be cool. Then I would use them\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUGH AUTO MERGE\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI didn\u0027t mean to offend people who use them, I\u0027m just ranting \u0027cause of my play style. Sorry!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nathair","CreatedById":102894,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T00:22:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222458990\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221458087063\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002285437\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Voculus\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 minutes ago, Voculus said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/PD3OgL1.jpg\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022PD3OgL1.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/PD3OgL1.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat mods have you got going there?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-03-16T00:23:04Z\u0022 title=\u002203/16/2016 12:23  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 16, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Nathair\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OrbitalBuzzsaw","CreatedById":158329,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T00:24:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do I delete a thread I made?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just Jim","CreatedById":148725,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T00:29:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI find IVA mode extremely helpful, and beautiful, when I\u0027m docking.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/hCIFAEf.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022hCIFAEf.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OrbitalBuzzsaw","CreatedById":158329,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T00:32:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do I take down my thread?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T00:34:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can sort of see your point, as there have been mods I\u0027ve wanted, or been waiting for, only to be told that, yeah, everything is done except IVAs... And several months, or even a year later, STILL no release... I think I\u0027ve even seen whole mods disappear and become abandoned, between being all done except IVAs or minor final touches, which take so long, or are so involved, that the dev abandons them and they NEVER get released and disappear into obscurity...\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nSo yeah, I do agree, that if a mod wants to do these beautiful, elaborate IVAs, then maybe THOSE parts should get done first, and then quit teasing a whole mod, just for iVAs... NO ONE LIKES A TEASE!! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:o\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_ohmy.png\u0022 title=\u0022:o\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-03-16T01:14:59Z\u0022 title=\u002203/16/2016 01:14  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 16, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Stone Blue\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bncrock","CreatedById":160319,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T00:44:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222458993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221458087104\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158329\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022OrbitalBuzzsaw\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n31 minutes ago, OrbitalBuzzsaw said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIVA hotkey is annoying. Trying to pull up, go into IVA. UGH!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFirst world problems.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222459026\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221458088347\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158329\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022OrbitalBuzzsaw\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 minutes ago, OrbitalBuzzsaw said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do I take down my thread?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhere do you think you\u0027re going? You made this thread, so ride it into obscurity.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Raptor9","CreatedById":67915,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T00:46:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222458993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221458087104\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158329\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022OrbitalBuzzsaw\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n37 minutes ago, OrbitalBuzzsaw said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI didn\u0027t mean to offend people who use them, I\u0027m just ranting \u0027cause of my play style. Sorry!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou didn\u0027t offend me, or anybody else it seems. \u00A0We were simply providing our views regarding IVA\u0027s based on our own play styles. \u00A0Personally, I can understand not wanting to release a mod until it fit the modders personal sense of completion. \u00A0As an avid craft file publisher,\u00A0I refuse to post a craft\u00A0file on KerbalX until I have the appropriate set of visual diagrams, description, and action groups clearly documented. \u00A0That\u0027s my personal standard of completion.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222459026\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221458088347\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158329\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022OrbitalBuzzsaw\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 minutes ago, OrbitalBuzzsaw said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do I take down my thread?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn your first post you asked who cares about IVA\u0027s and who uses them. \u00A0People answered your question...why do you want to delete the thread? \u00A0If you want to delete the thread so bad, contact one of the moderators in the Support section.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222459010\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221458087771\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022102894\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nathair\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n26 minutes ago, Nathair said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat mods have you got going there?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt appears to be Raster Prop Monitor.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-03-16T00:51:45Z\u0022 title=\u002203/16/2016 12:51  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 16, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Raptor9\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Andem","CreatedById":155578,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T01:07:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222459026\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221458088347\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158329\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022OrbitalBuzzsaw\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n32 minutes ago, OrbitalBuzzsaw said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do I take down my thread?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt can\u0027t be taken down, but you clearly got the answer to your question. I suggest you ask a moderator to lock it. In staying on topic, it is a little absurd to hold an update because of an IVA IMO.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OrbitalBuzzsaw","CreatedById":158329,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T01:09:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI give up. Hate on me all you want. I\u0027ll probably be banned within the hour.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T01:09:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFunny, I always just looked at IVAs as being decorative. I enjoyed looking around to see all the bins for trash, rubbish, junk, snacks, food, not food, and biohazards all mixed together. Trying to read the shopping lists on the post-it notes, to see what kerbals eat. I never even considered trying to\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Efly\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0a mission from an IVA. I use probe cores instead of pilots, anyway. But now I\u0027m definitely going to have to try an IVA flight or 10.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E@Raptor9:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u0022Elon Kerman\u0022?? LOL!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OrbitalBuzzsaw","CreatedById":158329,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T01:12:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222459029\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221458088444\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002277721\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stone Blue\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n37 minutes ago, Stone Blue said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can sort of see your point, as there have been mods I\u0027ve wanted, or been waiting for, only to be told that, yeah, everything is done except IVAs... And several months, or even a year later, STILL no release... I think I\u0027ve even seen whole mods disappear and become abandoned, between being all done except IVAs or minor final touches, which take so long, or are so involved, that the dev abandons them and they NEVER get released and disappear into obscurity...\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nSo yeah, I do agree, that if a mod wants to do these beautiful, elaborate IVAs, then maybe THOSE parts should get done first, and then quite teasing a whole mod, just for iVAs... NO ONE LIKES A TEASE!! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:o\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_ohmy.png\u0022 title=\u0022:o\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFINALLY, someone understands why I made this thread\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"razark","CreatedById":32993,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T01:13:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNobody\u0027s \u0022hating on\u0022 you.\u00A0 You asked a question, and you got an answer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe answer to your other question is you can\u0027t delete the thread.\u00A0 At this point, neither can a moderator.\u00A0 They can only delete them if there are no responses.\u00A0 The best you can get now is a locked thread.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Randazzo","CreatedById":136468,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T01:16:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222459077\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221458090578\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158329\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022OrbitalBuzzsaw\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, OrbitalBuzzsaw said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI give up. Hate on me all you want. I\u0027ll probably be banned within the hour.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot for this thread, unless you try real hard to make that happen. Also not seeing anybody hating on you, just disagreeing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDeep breaths.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you really want it locked:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/129807-need-your-own-thread-moved-or-locked-post-here/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-03-16T01:17:18Z\u0022 title=\u002203/16/2016 01:17  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 16, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Randazzo\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Andem","CreatedById":155578,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T01:19:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222459077\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022134293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221458090578\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158329\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022OrbitalBuzzsaw\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, OrbitalBuzzsaw said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI give up. Hate on me all you want. I\u0027ll probably be banned within the hour.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo hate from me. It was a legitimate frustration and one that is clearly shared by many members of the community. Honestly, check out the cutaway interior thread. I woild loke to apologize if anyone here made you feel cornered or in the wrong, because you weren\u0027t.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/125662-snark/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022125662\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/125662-snark/\u0022\u003E@Snark\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0It seems pretty clear that \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/158329-orbitalbuzzsaw/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022158329\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/158329-orbitalbuzzsaw/\u0022\u003E@OrbitalBuzzs